When your Daddy’s squadron was “the flying tigers” and your Mama is in branding…you wear all things tiger. 🐯❤️

Whelp, we are heading to Portugal in 7 days 🤣. Staying in Lisbon and Porto and hopefully some sort of dreamy spa escape out in the country.

Y’all have never steered me wrong before….Give me your best Portugal recs or tag someone who can📍❤️🙏🏼

A few years ago we traveled to Zurich for a partnership with @thedoldergrand. It had an incredible view of the city and lake below, absolutely incredible food, the most beautiful and comfortable rooms, a killer room service menu, and the most luxurious spa I had ever seen.

I remember leaving and thinking “I will never forget the last 2 days” and feeling so rested and content and inspired. 

Dylan and I head to Portugal this next week and I hope we can find a place that will give us that level of relaxation and restoration. We have waited 4 years to get back to Europe. And I am READY. If you know of any great spa hotels in Portugal, lemme know!⬇️
You are my angel, my darling, my star…and my love will find you, wherever you are.

These days…they’re nothing and everything at the same time. ❤️
